    <title>Algorithm4_Chapter1</title>
    <url>/Algorithm/Algorithm4-Chapter1/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>由于是出于复习的目的，且是第二次看 算法4 有些基础的部分笼统的复习一遍，并没有记录下来。</p>
<p>每篇题目均会与Leecode上的题目联系起来</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="背包、队列和栈"><a href="#背包、队列和栈" class="headerlink" title="背包、队列和栈"></a>背包、队列和栈</h2><ul>
<li>Bag（背包）：不支持从中删除元素的集合数据类型。背包的目的就是帮助用例收集元素并迭代遍历所有收集到的元素。</li>
<li>Queue（队列）：先进先出（FIFO）</li>
<li>Stack（栈）：先进后出（LIFO）<ul>
<li>浏览网页：点击超链接 -&gt; 入栈。 退回 -&gt; 出栈</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="算数表达式的求值（栈使用的例子）"><a href="#算数表达式的求值（栈使用的例子）" class="headerlink" title="算数表达式的求值（栈使用的例子）"></a>算数表达式的求值（栈使用的例子）</h3><p><a href="https://leetcode.com/problems/basic-calculator/">Leecode224 Basic Caculator</a></p>
<p>为了简单起见，这里定义的是 <strong>未省略括号</strong> 的算数表达式:</p>
<p>​                                ( 1 + ( ( 2 + 3 ) * ( 4 * 5 ) ) )</p>
<p>实现：</p>
<ol>
<li>new 出两个 Stack ，一个放操作数（1，2，3。。。） 另一个放 运算符（+，-，*，&#x2F;）</li>
<li>根据以下4种情况， 逐个送入栈中处理<ul>
<li>将 <strong>操作数</strong> 压入 <strong>操作数栈</strong></li>
<li>将 <strong>运算符</strong> 压入 <strong>运算符栈</strong></li>
<li>忽略 <strong>左括号</strong></li>
<li>如果遇到 <strong>右括号</strong>，弹出一个 <strong>运算符</strong>， 并弹出所需数量的 <strong>操作数</strong>， 将运算的结果，压回 <strong>操作数栈</strong></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<p>在处理完 <strong>最后一个右括号</strong> 之后，操作数栈上只有一个值，及我们所求值</p>
<p>代码实现:</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Dijkstra</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Evaluate</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> &#123; </span><br><span class="line">        Stack&lt;String&gt; ops  = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Stack</span>&lt;String&gt;();</span><br><span class="line">        Stack&lt;Double&gt; vals = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Stack</span>&lt;Double&gt;();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (!StdIn.isEmpty()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">s</span> <span class="operator">=</span> StdIn.readString();</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment">// 将 运算符 压入 运算符栈</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>      (s.equals(<span class="string">&quot;(&quot;</span>))               ; <span class="comment">// 遇到左括号，忽略</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (s.equals(<span class="string">&quot;+&quot;</span>))    ops.push(s);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (s.equals(<span class="string">&quot;-&quot;</span>))    ops.push(s);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (s.equals(<span class="string">&quot;*&quot;</span>))    ops.push(s);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (s.equals(<span class="string">&quot;/&quot;</span>))    ops.push(s);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (s.equals(<span class="string">&quot;sqrt&quot;</span>)) ops.push(s);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (s.equals(<span class="string">&quot;)&quot;</span>))  <span class="comment">// 遇到 右括号， 弹出运算符和操作数</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="type">String</span> <span class="variable">op</span> <span class="operator">=</span> ops.pop(); <span class="comment">// 弹出运算符</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="type">double</span> <span class="variable">v</span> <span class="operator">=</span> vals.pop(); <span class="comment">// 弹出第一个操作数</span></span><br><span class="line">              <span class="comment">// 弹出操作数并且，且根据 运算符， 弹出第二个操作数</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">if</span>      (op.equals(<span class="string">&quot;+&quot;</span>))    v = vals.pop() + v;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (op.equals(<span class="string">&quot;-&quot;</span>))    v = vals.pop() - v;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (op.equals(<span class="string">&quot;*&quot;</span>))    v = vals.pop() * v;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (op.equals(<span class="string">&quot;/&quot;</span>))    v = vals.pop() / v;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (op.equals(<span class="string">&quot;sqrt&quot;</span>)) v = Math.sqrt(v);</span><br><span class="line">              <span class="comment">// 将返回的值压回栈</span></span><br><span class="line">                vals.push(v);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">else</span> vals.push(Double.parseDouble(s)); <span class="comment">// 将操作数压入操作数栈</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125; </span><br><span class="line">        StdOut.println(vals.pop()); <span class="comment">// 返回结果</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>此代码是一个简单的 “解释器”： 一个能够解释给定字符串所表达的运算并计算得到结果的程序</p>
<blockquote>
<p>解释器（<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD/109997">英语</a>：Interpreter），又译为直译器，是一种电脑程序，能够把高级<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80">编程语言</a>一行一行直接转译运行。解释器不会一次把整个程序转译出来，只像一位“中间人”，每次运行程序时都要先转成另一种语言再作运行，因此解释器的程序运行速度比较缓慢。它每转译一行程序叙述就立刻运行，然后再转译下一行，再运行，如此不停地进行下去</p>
<p><img src="/Algorithm/Algorithm4-Chapter1/format,f_jpg.jpeg"></p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="集合数据类型的实现"><a href="#集合数据类型的实现" class="headerlink" title="集合数据类型的实现"></a>集合数据类型的实现</h3><h4 id="定容栈的实现"><a href="#定容栈的实现" class="headerlink" title="定容栈的实现"></a>定容栈的实现</h4><ul>
<li>定容栈： 容量固定的字符串栈的抽象类型</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">FixedCapacityStackOfStrings</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> String[] a;  <span class="comment">// holds the items</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">int</span> N;       <span class="comment">// number of items in stack</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// create an empty stack with given capacity</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="title function_">FixedCapacityStackOfStrings</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> capacity)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        a = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">String</span>[capacity];</span><br><span class="line">        N = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="title function_">isEmpty</span><span class="params">()</span>            &#123;  <span class="type">return</span> <span class="variable">N</span> <span class="operator">=</span>= <span class="number">0</span>;                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="title function_">isFull</span><span class="params">()</span>             &#123;  <span class="type">return</span> <span class="variable">N</span> <span class="operator">=</span>= a.length;             &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">push</span><span class="params">(String item)</span>       &#123;  a[N++] = item;                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> String <span class="title function_">pop</span><span class="params">()</span>                 &#123;  <span class="keyword">return</span> a[--N];                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> String <span class="title function_">peek</span><span class="params">()</span>                &#123;  <span class="keyword">return</span> a[N-<span class="number">1</span>];                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>缺点：只能有固定的String类型</p>
<h4 id="定容栈的改善（泛型）"><a href="#定容栈的改善（泛型）" class="headerlink" title="定容栈的改善（泛型）"></a>定容栈的改善（泛型）</h4><p>通过泛型来解决，只能存储String的问题</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">FixedCapacityStack</span>&lt;Item&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// Item 是一个类型参数，表示某种类型象征性的占位符</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>注意</strong>： 要通过类型转换来实现泛型数组的创建</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = (Item[]) <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Object</span>[cap];</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>泛型定容栈的代码实现</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">FixedCapacityStack</span>&lt;Item&gt;&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Item[] a;    <span class="comment">// holds the items</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">int</span> N;       <span class="comment">// number of items in stack</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// create an empty stack with given capacity</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="title function_">FixedCapacityStack</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> capacity)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        a = (Item[]) <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Object</span>[capacity];   <span class="comment">// no generic array creation</span></span><br><span class="line">        N = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="title function_">isEmpty</span><span class="params">()</span>          &#123;  <span class="type">return</span> <span class="variable">N</span> <span class="operator">=</span>= <span class="number">0</span>;                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">push</span><span class="params">(Item item)</span>       &#123;  a[N++] = item;                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> Item <span class="title function_">pop</span><span class="params">()</span>                 &#123;  <span class="keyword">return</span> a[--N];                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>缺点：栈的长度固定，如果要插入的元素过多，会导致超出索引范围。相反，若插入的元素过少，则会浪费空间</p>
<h4 id="定容栈的改善（调整数组大小）"><a href="#定容栈的改善（调整数组大小）" class="headerlink" title="定容栈的改善（调整数组大小）"></a>定容栈的改善（调整数组大小）</h4><p>通过一个resize的办法，实现调整数组的大小</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">resize</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> max)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  Item[] temp = (Item[]) <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Object</span>[max];</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span><span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; N;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    temp[i] = a[i];</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  a = temp;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>代码实现</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">ResizingArrayStack</span>&lt;Item&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Item[] a;    <span class="comment">// holds the items</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">int</span> N;       <span class="comment">// number of items in stack</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// create an empty stack with given capacity</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="title function_">ResizingArrayStack</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> capacity)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        a = (Item[]) <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Object</span>[capacity];   <span class="comment">// no generic array creation</span></span><br><span class="line">        N = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="title function_">isEmpty</span><span class="params">()</span>          &#123;  <span class="type">return</span> <span class="variable">N</span> <span class="operator">=</span>= <span class="number">0</span>;                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">push</span><span class="params">(Item item)</span>&#123; </span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span>(N == a.length) resize(<span class="number">2</span>*a.length);</span><br><span class="line">      a[N++] = item;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 修改pop，当栈的大小小于原来的1/4 时，数组长度减半</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> Item <span class="title function_">pop</span><span class="params">()</span>&#123;  </span><br><span class="line">      <span class="type">Item</span> <span class="variable">item</span> <span class="operator">=</span> a[N-<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">      a[N-<span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="literal">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      N--;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span>(N&gt;<span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; N == a.length/<span class="number">4</span>) resize(a.length/<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> item;               </span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">resize</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> max)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      Item[] temp = (Item[]) <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Object</span>[max];</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span><span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; N;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        temp[i] = a[i];</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      a = temp;</span><br><span class="line">  	 &#125;		</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="对象游离"><a href="#对象游离" class="headerlink" title="对象游离"></a>对象游离</h4><p>Java 的垃圾回收（GC）回收所有无法访问的内存，在实现 pop( ) 的过程中，被弹出元素的引用仍存在于数组之中。实际上这个元素不会再被访问，但是垃圾回收器无法知道这一点，除非改引用被覆盖。要实现这一点，将弹出元素的值设为null。这将覆盖无用的引用，并且使系统可以在用例使用完被弹出元素后回收它的内存。</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> Item <span class="title function_">pop</span><span class="params">()</span>&#123;  </span><br><span class="line">      <span class="type">Item</span> <span class="variable">item</span> <span class="operator">=</span> a[N-<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">      a[N-<span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="literal">null</span>; <span class="comment">// 防止loitering</span></span><br><span class="line">      N--;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span>(N&gt;<span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; N == a.length/<span class="number">4</span>) resize(a.length/<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> item;               </span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="定容栈的改善（迭代"><a href="#定容栈的改善（迭代" class="headerlink" title="定容栈的改善（迭代)"></a>定容栈的改善（迭代)</h4><p>要想实现可迭代的集合数据类型，必须满足：</p>
<ul>
<li>集合数据类型实现一个 iterator() 的方法，并且返回一个Iterator对象</li>
<li>Iterator类必须包含： hasNext() （返回boolean）和 next() （返回Item类型）</li>
</ul>
<p>在Java中，使用接口机制来指定一个类所要实现的办法。对于可迭代的类型，第一步就是在声明中加入对应的接口</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">ResizingArrayStack</span>&lt;Item&gt; <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title class_">Iterable</span>&lt;Item&gt; </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>通过观察 Iterable&lt;Item&gt; 可知，</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// java.lang 包下</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">interface</span> <span class="title class_">Iterable</span>&lt;Item&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  Iterator&lt;Item&gt; <span class="title function_">iterator</span><span class="params">()</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>要返回一个 Iterator。</p>
<p>Iterator是什么： 一个实现了 hasNext 和 next 方法的类的对象。由以下接口定义</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// java.util 包下</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">interface</span> <span class="title class_">Iterator</span>&lt;Item&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="title function_">hasNext</span><span class="params">()</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  Item <span class="title function_">next</span><span class="params">()</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">remove</span><span class="params">()</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="Stack（能够动态调整数组大小的实现）"><a href="#Stack（能够动态调整数组大小的实现）" class="headerlink" title="Stack（能够动态调整数组大小的实现）"></a>Stack（能够动态调整数组大小的实现）</h4><p><img src="/Algorithm/Algorithm4-Chapter1/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L20wXzQ1MDk3MTg2,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70.png"></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">ResizingArrayStack</span>&lt;Item&gt; <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title class_">Iterable</span>&lt;Item&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Item[] a;    <span class="comment">// holds the items</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">int</span> N;       <span class="comment">// number of items in stack</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// create an empty stack with given capacity</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="title function_">ResizingArrayStack</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> capacity)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        a = (Item[]) <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Object</span>[capacity];   <span class="comment">// no generic array creation</span></span><br><span class="line">        N = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="title function_">isEmpty</span><span class="params">()</span>          &#123;  <span class="type">return</span> <span class="variable">N</span> <span class="operator">=</span>= <span class="number">0</span>;                    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">push</span><span class="params">(Item item)</span>&#123; </span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span>(N == a.length) resize(<span class="number">2</span>*a.length);</span><br><span class="line">      a[N++] = item;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 修改pop，当栈的大小小于原来的1/4 时，数组长度减半</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> Item <span class="title function_">pop</span><span class="params">()</span>&#123;  </span><br><span class="line">      <span class="type">Item</span> <span class="variable">item</span> <span class="operator">=</span> a[N-<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">      a[N-<span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="literal">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">      N--;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">if</span>(N&gt;<span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; N == a.length/<span class="number">4</span>) resize(a.length/<span class="number">2</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">return</span> item;               </span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">resize</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> max)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      Item[] temp = (Item[]) <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Object</span>[max];</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span><span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; N;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        temp[i] = a[i];</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">      a = temp;</span><br><span class="line">  	 &#125;		</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="comment">// 返回迭代器</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> Iterator&lt;Item&gt; <span class="title function_">iterator</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">ReverseArrayIterator</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// an iterator, doesn&#x27;t implement remove() since it&#x27;s optional</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">ReverseArrayIterator</span> <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title class_">Iterator</span>&lt;Item&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> N;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="title function_">hasNext</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> i &gt; <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">remove</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">public</span> Item <span class="title function_">next</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (!hasNext()) <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">NoSuchElementException</span>();</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> a[--i];</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="Queue（能够动态调整数组大小的实现）"><a href="#Queue（能够动态调整数组大小的实现）" class="headerlink" title="Queue（能够动态调整数组大小的实现）"></a>Queue（能够动态调整数组大小的实现）</h4><p><img src="/Algorithm/Algorithm4-Chapter1/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L0t5cm90ZXg=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70.png"></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">ResizingArrayQueue</span>&lt;Item&gt; <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title class_">Iterable</span>&lt;Item&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// initial capacity of underlying resizing array</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">final</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">INIT_CAPACITY</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">8</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Item[] q;       <span class="comment">// queue elements</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">int</span> n;          <span class="comment">// number of elements on queue</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">int</span> first;      <span class="comment">// index of first element of queue</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">int</span> last;       <span class="comment">// index of next available slot</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="title function_">ResizingArrayQueue</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        q = (Item[]) <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Object</span>[INIT_CAPACITY];</span><br><span class="line">        n = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        first = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        last = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="title function_">isEmpty</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">return</span> <span class="variable">n</span> <span class="operator">=</span>= <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="title function_">size</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> n;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// resize the underlying array</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">resize</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">int</span> capacity)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">assert</span> capacity &gt;= n;</span><br><span class="line">        Item[] copy = (Item[]) <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Object</span>[capacity];</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            copy[i] = q[(first + i) % q.length];</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        q = copy;</span><br><span class="line">        first = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        last  = n;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">enqueue</span><span class="params">(Item item)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// double size of array if necessary and recopy to front of array</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (n == q.length) resize(<span class="number">2</span>*q.length);   <span class="comment">// double size of array if necessary</span></span><br><span class="line">        q[last++] = item;                        <span class="comment">// add item</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (last == q.length) last = <span class="number">0</span>;          <span class="comment">// wrap-around</span></span><br><span class="line">        n++;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> Item <span class="title function_">dequeue</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (isEmpty()) <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">NoSuchElementException</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Queue underflow&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">Item</span> <span class="variable">item</span> <span class="operator">=</span> q[first];</span><br><span class="line">        q[first] = <span class="literal">null</span>;                            <span class="comment">// to avoid loitering</span></span><br><span class="line">        n--;</span><br><span class="line">        first++;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (first == q.length) first = <span class="number">0</span>;           <span class="comment">// wrap-around</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// shrink size of array if necessary</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (n &gt; <span class="number">0</span> &amp;&amp; n == q.length/<span class="number">4</span>) resize(q.length/<span class="number">2</span>); </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> item;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> Item <span class="title function_">peek</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (isEmpty()) <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">NoSuchElementException</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Queue underflow&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> q[first];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> Iterator&lt;Item&gt; <span class="title function_">iterator</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">ArrayIterator</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">ArrayIterator</span> <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title class_">Iterator</span>&lt;Item&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="type">int</span> <span class="variable">i</span> <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="type">boolean</span> <span class="title function_">hasNext</span><span class="params">()</span>  &#123; <span class="keyword">return</span> i &lt; n;                               &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title function_">remove</span><span class="params">()</span>      &#123; <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">UnsupportedOperationException</span>();  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">public</span> Item <span class="title function_">next</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (!hasNext()) <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">NoSuchElementException</span>();</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">Item</span> <span class="variable">item</span> <span class="operator">=</span> q[(i + first) % q.length];</span><br><span class="line">            i++;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> item;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

